Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.00,0:00:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许攸啊 袁绍不是拒不发兵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还打了你二十军杖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.11,0:00:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不错 确有此事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.72,0:00:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那你怎么又到这里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.99,0:00:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德 说来你也许不信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.59,0:00:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我那二十军棍刚刚打完
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不成想主公那宝贝儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.50,0:00:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}忽然哭出声来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.70,0:00:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这下可把我们家主公给乐坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.30,0:00:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他抱起儿子跑出帐来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.41,0:00:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}连连向我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.41,0:00:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还赏了我二百两金子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.32,0:01:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一杖十两 值啊 值 值
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.80,0:01:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德 不瞒你说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.61,0:01:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我家主公就是这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.41,0:01:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小儿病情一旦好转
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.71,0:01:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他也变得心明眼亮起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.31,0:01:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}立刻接受了我的建议
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.31,0:01:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}令那颜良
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.52,0:01:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}亲统十万大军攻伐许昌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.62,0:01:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我哪 领兵五千先行一步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.52,0:01:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}特地来此打探徐州战局
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天意啊 天意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.10,0:01:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天意助曹不助刘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.70,0:02:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么 你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.71,0:02:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们不必攻打许昌了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.91,0:02:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州已经失陷了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.22,0:02:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操把大军调回许昌布防了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.62,0:02:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备 你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.80,0:02:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道你的兵马全都丧失了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那可是足足有八万人哪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.40,0:02:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兄弟离散 兵马丧失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}实话跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.41,0:02:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我连佩剑都失落了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.83,0:02:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想不到这个曹孟德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:03:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}居然有这么厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.90,0:03:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}汉贼不两立
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.01,0:03:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我刘备只要一息尚存
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就誓与曹操为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.62,0:03:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你乃当世真英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知你眼下有何打算
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.80,0:03:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}欲往何处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.71,0:03:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德 我倒有一个主意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.31,0:03:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}莫不如
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你随我投奔我家主公袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.72,0:03:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以图日后再举
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你意下如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道我还要继续寄人篱下么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你不妨平心静气地想一想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.71,0:04:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当今天下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.41,0:04:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然是群雄纷争
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.01,0:04:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但真正能够剿灭曹贼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}并匡扶汉室者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.42,0:04:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}眼下除了我家主公
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁本初之外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.02,0:04:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还能有谁呀 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多谢先生指教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下愿投袁公
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.61,0:04:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许先生 主公得知刘备前来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.63,0:05:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}立刻出营十里相迎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.63,0:05:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公何在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}皇叔啊 我曾经跟你说过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我家这个主公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}庸弱时啊庸弱得确实让人惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.81,0:05:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是一旦圣明起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.71,0:05:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那也圣明得让人惊讶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 刘皇叔到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.01,0:06:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}败军之将刘备 拜见袁大将军
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘皇叔快快请起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你呀是个仁义之君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.92,0:06:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}贤名满天下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我早就想与你共图大业了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.03,0:06:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今日相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁某深感欣慰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.34,0:06:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备只有一个心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}助袁公剿灭曹贼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}匡扶大汉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.01,0:06:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是你我共同的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来 且随我回营
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.82,0:06:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}容我为你摆酒洗尘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.32,0:06:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然后共商灭曹大计 走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.22,0:06:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}皇叔 请
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 刘备大部分兵马被歼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:07:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}降者三万多 都是我军旧部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍的援军行进到距徐州三十里处
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不战而退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.62,0:07:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀丞相 现在小沛也已经被末将拿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.52,0:07:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}唯有下邳还在关羽手中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 下邳已是一座孤城
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.93,0:07:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}肯定是兵无斗志
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末将愿领一支精兵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.43,0:07:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}五日之内把它拿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下邳由关羽把守
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我若强攻 他必战死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不瞒你们说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.93,0:08:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备所有部将当中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.83,0:08:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我最喜爱关羽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.14,0:08:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此人武艺高强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.44,0:08:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又极为忠义
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}若是能归降我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}胜得十万雄兵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 臣有一计
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}或许可行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说来听听
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}既然关羽是忠义之士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对付这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.53,0:09:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不可力战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}莫不如将他引入走投无路之地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.14,0:09:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再以忠义相诱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.32,0:09:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公已经十几天没消息了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.32,0:09:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也不知道战况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果今日再无消息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我一定要出城打探
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军莫要心急
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其实这没有消息就是好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这说明城池还在主公手里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹军撤了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.74,0:09:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是为何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.64,0:09:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是福还是祸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.85,0:09:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军请看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那里有几个残兵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.12,0:10:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像是咱们的军士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.02,0:10:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}开城 叫他们进来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.32,0:10:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快 开城门
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.94,0:10:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们是哪一部的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.94,0:10:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军 关将军 关将军
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们是张冀德将军的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.04,0:10:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}随主公驻防徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公太平吗 徐州怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.75,0:10:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀将军
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公和张将军
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都被围困在了芒砀山上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}血战待援
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.92,0:10:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.62,0:10:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}前天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.42,0:10:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公带兵夜袭曹营
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不料中了那曹贼的奸计
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.73,0:10:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被围困在芒砀山上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}召集所有骑兵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}随我杀往芒砀山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.13,0:10:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}慢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}备马 取我兵器来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}慢慢慢 将军 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军莫要心急
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.24,0:10:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可否先派数骑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.24,0:10:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}出城打探虚实再说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:10:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公有难 生死不明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.35,0:11:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我早到一刻是一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}芒砀山距此三十多里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}眨眼便到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果主公真的被困于芒砀山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.32,0:11:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么山下肯定布满了曹操的重兵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军只有两千铁骑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如何解得了主公之围啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.33,0:11:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公和三弟在那血战
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.83,0:11:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你难道让我置他们于死地而不顾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不不不 我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.04,0:11:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是说 曹贼兵多 咱们将寡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.34,0:11:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一旦出击 咱们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.94,0:11:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}任他千军万马
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也要救出主公和三弟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果救不回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就和他们同死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.34,0:12:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看来这里确实是发生过激战
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.44,0:12:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公他恐怕凶多吉少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}报 报 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}山上都已经巡遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仍不见主公的踪迹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不好了将军
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.96,0:12:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们被曹军包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.83,0:13:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}随我杀下山去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.33,0:13:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}救回主公
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}杀下山去 救回主公
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}杀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.96,0:13:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}报 主公 关羽三次突围
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都被我们万箭射回
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们死伤不少
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.23,0:13:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看来是无力再冲了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.64,0:13:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}山上又没有水源
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.64,0:13:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}料想关羽他们难以久持啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}张辽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末将在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.65,0:13:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我听说你和关羽交情不错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.95,0:13:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.65,0:13:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关羽他为人忠义 武艺高强
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.75,0:13:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末将与他是旧友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.15,0:13:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想劳你上山 劝降关羽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.26,0:13:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.76,0:14:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 末将断断不敢奉命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 为何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.43,0:14:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我了解他的性子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.33,0:14:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关羽他是宁可战死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也不肯归降的那种人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就是浑身是嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也说不动他呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}文远将军啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请听我言
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}假如关羽真要战死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你就指责他说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.32,0:14:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.15,0:14:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}则有三项罪过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.36,0:14:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果不死 则有三种方便
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军请看 山下有人上来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.65,0:15:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像是曹军将领
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.96,0:15:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}文远兄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.06,0:15:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是来争斗的呢还是来相助的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.63,0:15:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下来和云长兄共谋一醉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我正渴着哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.87,0:15:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.33,0:15:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是曹丞相特意送给关将军的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.24,0:15:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}云长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.55,0:16:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你一出城
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相就收复了下邳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.05,0:16:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}云长不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我军进城以后 秋毫无犯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}特别是刘玄德的府宅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.96,0:16:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}更是太平无事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相早就下了严令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.86,0:16:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}各级将士只准在刘府外守护
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不得擅入
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁要是胆敢擅入刘府一步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}立斩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}失了下邳 是我关某之罪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.74,0:16:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}文远兄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.25,0:16:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请你看在你我多年相交的分上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请直言相告
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我兄长他们究竟怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备早已大败
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.36,0:16:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}残余将士都归顺了曹丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.26,0:16:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有人看见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.46,0:16:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备单骑逃进了深山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.16,0:16:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}至今不知生死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.14,0:17:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}云长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也容我问你一句
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以你现在的情况来看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果丞相号令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}山下的五万铁骑冲锋的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你能破围而出吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关某不能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.75,0:17:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那你准备怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.66,0:17:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请你转告曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.76,0:17:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喝下这壶酒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.66,0:17:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我关某便提刀下山
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.26,0:17:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先斩他三百将士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他也可来取我的头颅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}云长兄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.64,0:17:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此时此刻 死是易事 活着才难
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}云长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你要是一死了之的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.85,0:17:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}则死有三罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哪三罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.66,0:17:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第一罪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.66,0:17:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们刘关张三结义
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当年在桃园的时候曾立下誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.36,0:17:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}同年同月同日死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.77,0:18:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备虽然兵败
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.07,0:18:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但生死未知
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.27,0:18:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军试想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.47,0:18:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果你的兄长还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.17,0:18:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你却先死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}岂不有违当年的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第二罪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.85,0:18:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备将二位夫人托付于你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.75,0:18:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你快意一死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.35,0:18:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抛下二位夫人怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.15,0:18:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道把她们交到乱兵手中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玷污贞操吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.26,0:18:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你不是说 曹操有令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不能踏入刘府一步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.36,0:18:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}违者斩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.37,0:18:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是因为有你关云长健在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.57,0:18:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相爱才敬你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.57,0:18:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果你死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.17,0:18:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只怕没有人能管得住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.27,0:18:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那些骄兵悍将了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.44,0:18:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你先不要着急
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.94,0:18:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听我把话说完
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第三罪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.75,0:18:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们兄弟三人立志要匡扶汉室
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.75,0:18:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可如今枭雄未除 天下未定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你却先死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}试问
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.46,0:19:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在九泉之下如何去见天子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如何去见兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}云长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这死后的三罪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下不得不说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.47,0:19:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不能求死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.37,0:19:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又该当如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.57,0:19:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听我说 这死有三罪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}生却有三便
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.75,0:19:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哪三便
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.15,0:19:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你现在是身陷重围
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.42,0:19:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}走投无路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不如暂时先归顺曹丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.16,0:19:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}待日后打听到刘备的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.56,0:19:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再去投奔他不迟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.66,0:19:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如此 生有三便
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.06,0:19:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第一 可以保证二位嫂夫人的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.07,0:19:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第二 不负当年桃园之誓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第三 留得英雄之躯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}待来日匡扶大汉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有道理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也有三约
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.37,0:20:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果他同意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.87,0:20:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我立刻卸甲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.27,0:20:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果他不同意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我宁可负三罪而死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}云长请讲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第一 我只降汉帝 不降曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.92,0:20:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第二 请丞相善待我的二位嫂嫂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.86,0:20:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第三 一旦有我兄长下落
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,0:20:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}无论天涯海角
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我都要寻他而去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.27,0:20:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以上三约
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.67,0:20:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}缺了任何一条
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.17,0:20:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是万万不降
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.75,0:21:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}文远 情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.05,0:21:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相 关羽说了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.96,0:21:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要他归降 他有三约
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 说我听听
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.56,0:21:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第一 他只降汉帝 不降主公
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是朝廷丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.47,0:21:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}降汉就是降我 准了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第二 善待他的二位嫂夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.87,0:21:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}各级军士不得擅自入门
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.88,0:21:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我岂止会善待两位刘夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我还会加倍地奉养她们 准
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关羽的第三条
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是他一旦知道了刘备的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.65,0:21:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}纵然是天涯海角
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.25,0:21:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也要投他而去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.86,0:21:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要关羽何用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.86,0:21:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个却难以答应
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.27,0:22:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.17,0:22:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末将想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备对关羽无非是厚恩而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.38,0:22:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果丞相对关羽恩典更厚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.58,0:22:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}时间久了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.08,0:22:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关羽必被感化
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.08,0:22:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再说 刘备生死不明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.85,0:22:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不一定还在人间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.46,0:22:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此话有理
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.66,0:22:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}世人只知道曹某之威
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.07,0:22:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知道曹某的恩典更重于威严
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.87,0:22:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这第三约 准了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.07,0:22:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.47,0:22:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 传令退军十里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.58,0:22:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让关羽下山回城
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.58,0:22:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相 这事倒令人担心哪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.28,0:22:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关羽他要降便降
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.89,0:22:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相不可放他回城啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.45,0:22:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为何
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.46,0:22:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果关羽乘机脱逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.86,0:22:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那可是龙入大海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.46,0:22:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这就是我给他的第一道恩典
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.96,0:23:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让他回城
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.37,0:23:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.47,0:23:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关羽决不会背约逃生的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.27,0:23:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.58,0:23:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末将关羽 拜见丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.45,0:23:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快快请起 快快请起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.96,0:24:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我得关云长 胜过十万雄兵
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.66,0:24:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.57,0:24:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末将的归降三约
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.37,0:24:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请丞相莫忘
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.57,0:24:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当然
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.57,0:24:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹某一言 驷马难追
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.87,0:24:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}日后 如有兄长下落
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.08,0:24:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}无论天涯海角
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.18,0:24:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我定当前去相会
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.68,0:24:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}云长 你就放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.79,0:26:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}公瑾觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.79,0:26:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这首曲子弹奏得如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.00,0:26:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}琴曲曼妙传神
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.40,0:26:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让人陶醉
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.27,0:26:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.77,0:26:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这曲中间弹错了一个音调
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.27,0:26:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}公瑾真是精通音律啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.98,0:26:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}区区的一个音调
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.18,0:26:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都逃不过你的耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.28,0:26:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我只是略懂一二而已
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.08,0:26:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是不知
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.39,0:26:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是何人在弹奏这首曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.89,0:26:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我与主公一同前往
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.69,0:26:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一看便知
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.79,0:26:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 随我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.89,0:27:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二位将军今日造访小宅
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.00,0:27:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知有何事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.80,0:27:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}前些时日
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.87,0:27:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我与主公在竹林中
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.87,0:27:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听到有人在弹奏琴曲
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.07,0:27:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}琴声曼妙让人陶醉
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.77,0:27:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}后来得知是乔家女儿在弹奏
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.18,0:27:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以今日特意前来拜访
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.98,0:27:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不错
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.48,0:27:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那日我与公瑾
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.88,0:27:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被竹林当中的琴声所吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.68,0:27:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今日想见一见弹奏琴曲的人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.89,0:27:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}烦请乔公满足我们的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.09,0:27:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.59,0:27:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过不瞒将军
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.50,0:27:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老朽家有两女
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.20,0:28:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都通些音律
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.20,0:28:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知道将军说的是哪一个
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.47,0:28:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}乔公有两女个儿
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.17,0:28:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对 长女叫大乔
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.18,0:28:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二女叫小乔
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.28,0:28:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她们都喜欢在竹林里练习琴曲
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.79,0:28:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们只是听到了琴曲
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.69,0:28:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}并未见到弹奏琴曲之人
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.89,0:28:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是听到那日弹奏的古曲江南
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.99,0:28:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}错了一个音调
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.80,0:28:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}既然这样
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.00,0:28:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我让大乔小乔出来见过二位将军
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.80,0:28:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一问便知
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.00,0:28:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}乔公且慢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.87,0:28:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}公谨
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.27,0:28:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}世人都说你精通音律
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.08,0:28:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我看这样好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.78,0:28:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让大乔和小乔同时弹奏一支曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.28,0:28:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}由你来听辨
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.08,0:28:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看看那天在竹林当中弹奏的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.88,0:28:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.59,0:28:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}公瑾意下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.29,0:29:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.29,0:29:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我倒愿意一试
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.90,0:29:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但不知乔公的二位小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.00,0:29:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是否愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.60,0:30:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}公瑾 如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.80,0:30:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此曲堪称绝伦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.50,0:30:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大乔 小乔
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.81,0:30:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快出来见过二位将军
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.18,0:30:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}见过二位将军
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.59,0:30:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.09,0:30:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}世上竟有如此美妙的女子
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.51,0:30:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 袁术那个门客
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.01,0:31:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还是从轻发落吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.68,0:31:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此事公瑾不用多言
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.98,0:31:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来来来
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.98,0:31:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看看我收集的这些琴谱
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.20,0:31:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.60,0:31:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}何时开始喜欢上收集琴谱了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.60,0:31:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也想像公瑾一样
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.90,0:31:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}学习一些音律
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.21,0:31:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我看伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.31,0:31:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是真心要学习音律吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.09,0:31:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看来知我者莫如公瑾也
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.39,0:31:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那日你我一同去乔家
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.80,0:31:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你觉得乔公的大乔小乔如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.50,0:31:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}两个人都有伯牙子期之才
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.60,0:32:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}倾国倾城之容
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.31,0:32:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}称得上一代佳人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.51,0:32:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那公瑾以为
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.41,0:32:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果你我兄弟二人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.58,0:32:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能娶大乔小乔为妻
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.29,0:32:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如何
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.19,0:32:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那可谓英雄佳人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.49,0:32:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天作之合
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.59,0:32:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这些琴谱就是聘礼
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.50,0:32:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要给你我兄弟二人求亲
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.89,0:32:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相口谕
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.09,0:32:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今日端午节 特赠关将军
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.99,0:32:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}金五十 美玉三件
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.79,0:32:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}钱三千 绸缎二十匹
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.60,0:33:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关羽拜谢丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.20,0:33:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相口谕
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.40,0:33:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关羽征战多年 鞍马徒劳
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.60,0:33:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}应稍事休息
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.31,0:33:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}特赠江南美女十名 早晚侍候
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.51,0:33:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}替我转告丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.81,0:33:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}美女万万使不得 使不得
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.92,0:33:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相另有口谕
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.42,0:33:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关羽如果说他使不得
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.09,0:33:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就让他自行安排吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.89,0:33:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.89,0:33:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相口谕在下已传达完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.79,0:33:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谨告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.40,0:33:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹丞相三日一小宴 五日一大宴
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.50,0:33:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}金银绸缎 玉器豪宅
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.01,0:33:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}更是赏赐不断
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.11,0:33:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今日竟然又送来了一群美女
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.11,0:33:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这让我如何收受得了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.21,0:33:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下从军这么多年了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.72,0:33:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也没见过这么多的赏赐
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.52,0:33:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这也是将军的福气 收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.49,0:33:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}东西也就罢了 美女万万使不得
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.89,0:34:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}送她们回去
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.79,0:34:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操把话都说到前头了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.80,0:34:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军要是不收呢也不合适
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.10,0:34:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过在下想
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.00,0:34:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果把这些美女安排在后堂
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.10,0:34:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}专门伺候主公的夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.01,0:34:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}甚好 甚好 带她们去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.61,0:34:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命 来 跟我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.99,0:34:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个肉鲜美无比
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.70,0:34:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么做出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.20,0:34:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀丞相 这是半岁的小鹿肉
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.40,0:34:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}庖厨们用了九种佐料
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.90,0:34:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}文火烹出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.40,0:34:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.40,0:34:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还有大半罐
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.71,0:34:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给云长送去
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.21,0:34:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}告诉他 这是半岁的小鹿肉
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.41,0:34:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}鲜美无比 不可不尝
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.21,0:34:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.32,0:34:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}连炉子一块端走
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.62,0:35:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不可在半道上凉了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.02,0:35:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.49,0:35:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}闪开 闪开 别烫着喽
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.59,0:35:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相赏关将军鹿肉
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.80,0:35:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.70,0:35:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奴才已把鹿肉给关将军送去了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.00,0:35:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关将军拜谢丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.41,0:35:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我刚想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.81,0:35:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}食肉断断不可无酒
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.61,0:35:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此酒香醇清冽
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.21,0:35:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正好可以用来佐食鹿肉
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.31,0:35:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快给云长送去
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.62,0:35:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}务必要在他吃完鹿肉之前送到
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.42,0:35:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.62,0:35:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相赏关将军美酒
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.89,0:35:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要在鹿肉食完前送到
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.70,0:35:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相赏关将军美酒
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.70,0:35:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要在鹿肉食完前送到
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.60,0:35:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听到了没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.61,0:36:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相衣食冷暖皆惦记着关羽
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.21,0:36:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我等出生入死多年
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.02,0:36:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还不如一个降将啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.30,0:36:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恭喜关将军了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.81,0:36:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}文远兄 关某何喜之有
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.82,0:36:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相在一餐之间
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.32,0:36:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}两次赠将军鹿肉美酒
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.62,0:36:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相府上下无不为之惊叹
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.02,0:36:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}云长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.53,0:36:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相对你可是求贤若渴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.50,0:36:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相待我的确恩重如山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.70,0:37:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可正是这座山
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.11,0:37:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}压得我是喘不过气来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.41,0:37:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}云长为何这样讲
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.71,0:37:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关某自顺曹以来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.98,0:37:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相三日一小宴 五日一大宴
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.72,0:37:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}金银珠宝玉器豪宅
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.42,0:37:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}更是赏赐不断
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.83,0:37:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而我 身无尺寸之功
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.20,0:37:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却有折腰之耻
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.80,0:37:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我何以回报
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.10,0:37:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相这山一般的大恩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.41,0:37:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}越是美味佳酿 越是骨鲠在喉
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.81,0:37:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这么说我就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.12,0:37:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难怪你每天酒肉美食
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.92,0:37:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不但没有吃胖
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.52,0:37:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}反而日渐憔悴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.32,0:37:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}更让我担心的是
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.13,0:37:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兄长和三弟至今下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.73,0:37:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}生死不知
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.63,0:38:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}云长不必焦虑
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.00,0:38:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有道是 富贵有命 生死在天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.51,0:38:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相待你如此恩宠
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.71,0:38:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}羡慕死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.01,0:38:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}云长我俩共饮几杯
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.92,0:38:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这么好的酒肉美食
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.22,0:38:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不吃的话太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.02,0:38:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}云长 快来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.83,0:38:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关羽被丞相的大恩
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.23,0:38:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}压得是喘不过气来了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.63,0:38:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}整日的心理忐忑
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.93,0:38:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他发愁的是
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.23,0:38:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}自己身无尺寸之功
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.00,0:38:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却有折腰之辱
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.70,0:38:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将来如何能报答
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.50,0:38:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相像山一般厚重的大恩
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.21,0:38:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关羽他为此十分发愁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.31,0:38:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}愁得好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.71,0:38:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这正是我所希望的效果
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.92,0:38:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要先让关羽感动
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.12,0:38:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不安 内疚 继之知恩图报
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.32,0:39:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最后倾心拜服
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.03,0:39:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相的恩威 天下之冠
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.33,0:39:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可以说世上无人能比
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.63,0:39:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.03,0:39:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.70,0:39:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关羽他仍然还牵挂念着刘备和张飞
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.91,0:39:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可以说是日夜悬心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.31,0:39:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.81,0:39:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关羽对刘备的忠义之心
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.01,0:39:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}并没有改变
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.81,0:39:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}忠义有何不好呢 好得很
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.52,0:39:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有忠肝义胆 谈何英雄壮士
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.82,0:39:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我要把他对刘备的忠肝义胆
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.73,0:39:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}变成对我的忠肝义胆
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.93,0:39:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}文远啊 你瞧着
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.53,0:39:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明日我要送他一样宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.33,0:39:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他见了肯定感动得给我跪下
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.41,0:39:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.51,0:39:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你拭目以待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.82,0:40:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我令关羽随我行猎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.72,0:40:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此刻时辰已到
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.33,0:40:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他怎么还不来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.53,0:40:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相放心
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.73,0:40:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关羽他早已领命 一定会到
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.82,0:40:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关羽拜见丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.53,0:40:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}云长为何迟误啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.53,0:40:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下的战马过于瘦弱
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.44,0:40:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}马速缓慢 所以来迟
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.24,0:40:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请丞相恕罪
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.51,0:41:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}战马如同将军的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.61,0:41:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你驰骋沙场多年
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.82,0:41:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么会连一匹骏马都没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.22,0:41:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相所言极是
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.52,0:41:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}战马如同将士的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.73,0:41:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如意座骑可遇不可求
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.23,0:41:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说得好 说得真好
